// Stubbed for PF1e: this mechanic referenced macros / stats from the
// inherited pf2e scaffold that do not exist in PF1e. Stubbing to a
// no-op sequence preserves the event_names registration so the loader
// still sees a handler; the event will simply not change state.
mechanic change_skill_sort_to_ability(event_names = "sort_by_name") =
  sequence(effects = []);
